---
title: Cheesy Beef Empanada Pockets with Balsamic Glazed Rocket Salad
description: These Cheesy Beef Empanada Pockets are a crowd pleaser and are one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-beef-empanada-pockets-d73a35e2-249cd52e.jpg
